  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Such imitation games are commonly referred to as \"Turing-style tests. \"",
    "One of the best-known Turing-style tests is the CAPTCHA (Ahn et al., 2003).",
    "This test is often referred to as a \"reverse Turing Test, \" since the role of the interrogator is carried out by a machine rather than a human.",
    "The Loebner Prize Competition used another variation on Turing's test to identify the best chatbot (Moor, 2001).",
    "The Feigenbaum Test (Feigenbaum, 2003) represents yet another Turing-style test."
  ],
